{
  "texts": [
    "Initially, we adjust the sentence dimensionality D, as well as the thresholds σ and γ of y i, while maintaining λ as a constant.",
    "Otherwise, we adjust λ while keeping the other parameters at fixed values.",
    "When calculating the values of MSE and Pcc, each sentence pair yields only a single experimental similarity value.",
    "For all sentence pairs that meet the recalculation criteria, the recalculated value will replace the initially computed value.",
    "In essence, the recomputed outcomes from SQE or WQE will supersede the AQE results."
  ]
}